Package: keystone-hybrid-backend
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  keystone
Description: LDAP/SQL hybrid Identity/Assignment drivers for Keystone
 Hybrid identity and assignment drivers for keystone allow local accounts
 to be stored in SQL and remote accounts in LDAP. Requires clients have
 python-keystoneclient (>= 0.4.0) in order to be functional. NOTE: The
 hybrid Assignment driver requires configuration in the python file.
